{"tid":1660752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣新角度 劉備齊齊做","createTime":"2019-10-17T16:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T16:53:01.000Z","uid":9962,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0747d7d6981e3650b0aba7c5f978f873d28342","tid":1660752,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:33:15.000Z","msg":"大家一直以嚟好辛苦咁對抗政府、極權、警黑，成果舉世矚目，甚至輸出海外。<br />\n<br />\n大部分人都connect到，依然仲有少部份自稱「中立」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但唔緊要，我地用「正義感」將佢地攞埋返嚟！<br />\n<br />\n三國嘅劉備只有一樣嘢最出名，「仁義、正義」。佢做過乜嘢咁仁義？十問九個都唔知，但依然無阻佢成為對抗極權、邪惡曹操嘅KOL <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由今日開始，描寫我地嘅正義、呢四個月為香港帶嚟乜嘢改變！光復屯公、調整樓價等等.. 描寫對家對我地嘅逼害，逼死義士、濫暴濫捕、對策離地！<br />\n<br />\n雖然好多嘢大家已經知，但溫故知新，要令所有人對呢四個月嘅來龍去脈一清二楚"},{"pid":"626ebd8b182b34c3984c0dec49190590e6a744d8","tid":1660752,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:33:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHH8FUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHH8FUF.jpg&h=3fd66e79&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"13b1f8190760340f7d82d80f2cca3fc575261d25","tid":1660752,"uid":9962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:33:56.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇用 推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6dd0e4846927f7ae6bae6a973f493ec15373b7c","tid":1660752,"uid":258118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線+英語戰線]要贏，就要有自己既傳媒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1660726\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1660726</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c489b718cbfb1268dd2e4234d91a4274787f0d32","tid":1660752,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:36:46.000Z","msg":"推 有冇idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb98c72ffb63f89e6695e8b8e1e6257d1815581","tid":16